He clutched her wrists and examined her, cautiously checking for any signs of harm. This simple action started the process. A surge of electricity shot through them both, as the pulling sensation returned to their chests. Malayjah closed her eyes and allowed the strength of the bond to have it's way with her. Zy'Phon had to bite down on his tongue to keep himself from squirming uncontrollably. The feeling was no doubt a pleasurable one, but that pleasure came with massive amounts of pain. Zy'Phon, who had a body more durable than Malayjah's inhaled deeply as the pain cascaded through him. Malayjah let out several cries of agony.The young demon in front of her felt excruciating discomfort at the sound of it. Once the bond calmed itself, Zy'Phon loosened his grip on Malayjah.

Without letting go of her wrists he kneeled before her, gazing straight into those big brown eyes. "I am now your faithful guardian. I promise to protect you until the day I die. I will be loyal to you and only you."
